cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a deep learning framework for spatio-temporal forecasting, which involves the integration of spatial and temporal characteristics. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and social and information networks (cs.SI). However, given the focus on deep learning and neural networks, as well as the use of hypernetworks, cs.LG and cs.NE are the most likely sub-categories.
